WEBVTT

00:08:30.127 --> 00:08:32.306
Vnútorná bolesť vyjde vždy na povrch.

00:08:33.068 --> 00:08:34.468
Vždy.

00:08:34.863 --> 00:08:36.395
A kto za to zaplatí?

00:08:37.244 --> 00:08:38.649
My.

00:08:38.673 --> 00:08:39.823
Naše deti,

00:08:40.696 --> 00:08:41.846
naši kolegovia,

00:08:43.354 --> 00:08:45.154
naše komunity.

00:08:49.354 --> 00:08:50.766
Prosím, nechápte ma zle.

00:08:51.203 --> 00:08:52.841
Nie som proti šťastiu.

00:08:54.213 --> 00:08:55.522
Rada som šťastná.

00:08:55.546 --> 00:08:57.133
Som celkom šťastná osoba.

00:08:58.181 --> 00:09:03.958
Ale keď potláčame prirodzené emócie
a snažíme sa o falošnú pozitivitu,